9
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,960
Far brighter.

10
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,040
Lord Commander, here.

11
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,840
Mr. Han,

12
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,600
on such a full moon night,

13
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,960
do you also think of

14
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,880
your family like I do?

15
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,080
I...

