My parents died at young age.

17
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,480
[I have no family left.]

18
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,160
Once I marry Caiwei,

19
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,880
the Yans will be my family.

20
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,480
Right, right.

21
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,240
Parents gone,

22
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,560
