28
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,240
That's right.

29
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,000
No need for that.

30
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,440
I left home to study at a young age.

31
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:08,120
