32
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,040
[As long as we truly love each other,]

33
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:10,840
that's enough.

34
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,320
[As for formalities,]

35
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,560
they don't matter to me.

36
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:17,880
Is that so?

37
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,040
I can't help but feel

38
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,240
that these formalities

39
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:21,640
are quite necessary.

40
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,560
Even if you're truly in love,

41
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,680
you should still hope to

42
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,720
gain recognition and blessings

43
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,080
from each other's family and friends.

44
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,120
[More importantly,]

45
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,360
this will help you have a clear

46
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,080
understanding of your background

47
00:04:43,039 --> 00:04:44,320
and avoid any deception.

48
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,080
That's true.

49
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,720
But actually, my marriage wasn't

50
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,440
hindered by such formalities.

51
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,560
What matters the most is that Mr. Han

52
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,680
is deeply devoted to my sister.

53
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,240
[It's getting late,]

54
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,080
[and a bit chilly.]

55
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:23,880
How about

56
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,120
