57
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,480
Yes.

58
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,760
We shall take our leave.

59
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,560
Right, right.

60
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:41,960
[Lord Commander,]

61
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,560
we'll head back now.

62
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:45,880
Let's go.

63
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:46,880
Mr. Han.

64
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,720
Should your love be sincere

65
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,760
and reciprocated,

66
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,000
[there is no need to dread openness.]

67
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,840
You should face the future together.

68
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:02,840
My love,

69
